      "writtenOn": "2017-07-24T20:05:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I guess this could be a liveness.  In InfluxDB land, we uploaded the size of the backup (which was potentially interesting as well) and alerted when that data stopped being there.  We do the same thing here, alert if the backup size over the last 25 hours is 0 (i.e. not happening)\n\nDo you think we should switch to a liveness, given the backup service should almost always be running?",
